# Idle / Clicker — Project Configuration

## Project Overview
- **Unity Version:** 2022.3 LTS
- **Render Pipeline:** URP (mobile optimized)
- **Genre:** Idle / clicker / incremental
- **Target Platform:** iOS + Android
- **Target FPS:** 30 (battery-friendly, idle game)

## Architecture

### Assembly Structure
```
MyGame.Core         — events, utilities, big number math
MyGame.Economy      — currencies, generators, upgrades, prestige
MyGame.Gameplay     — tap handler, automation, milestones
MyGame.Meta         — offline progress, daily rewards, achievements
MyGame.UI           — currency display, upgrade list, prestige screen
MyGame.Systems      — audio, save, ads, IAP, analytics, notifications
```

### Key Systems
- **Currency System** — multiple currencies (gold, gems, prestige tokens)
- **Generator System** — auto-income sources, upgradeable
- **Upgrade System** — exponential cost scaling (cost × 1.15^level)
- **Tap Income** — tap to earn, upgradeable tap value
- **Offline Progress** — calculate earnings while away (capped at 8hrs, 50% efficiency)
- **Prestige System** — reset progress for permanent multipliers
- **Daily Rewards** — consecutive day bonuses
- **Monetization** — rewarded ads (2x offline, 2x income boost), IAP (currency packs)

### Scene Structure
- `S_Bootstrap` — persistent services (save, ads, IAP, notifications)
- `S_Game` — single scene (main game + all UI overlays)

## Skills to Load
- `mobile` — ASTC textures, draw call budget, thermal management, safe areas
- `idle-clicker` — big numbers, offline progress, prestige, upgrade trees
- `save-system` — auto-save on every purchase, offline time tracking
- `ui-toolkit` — upgrade lists, currency displays, animated counters
- `audio` — satisfying tap sounds, milestone fanfares
- `dotween` — number counter animations, UI transitions

## Rules
Follow all rules in `.codex-legacy/rules/`.

## Key Conventions
- **Big numbers** — use formatted display (1.23K, 4.56M, 7.89B, etc.)
- **Auto-save** — save on every purchase, OnApplicationPause, OnApplicationQuit
- **Offline progress** — calculate on launch, show "Welcome back!" popup
- **30fps cap** — idle games don't need 60fps, saves battery
- **Minimal Update** — update currency display every 0.1s, not every frame
- **Exponential scaling** — both costs and rewards grow exponentially
- **No skill required** — progress = time + strategic upgrade choices
- **Safe area** — all UI respects Screen.safeArea
- **Notification hooks** — remind players to collect offline earnings

## Input Map
```
Player:
  Tap to Earn — Primary Touch
  Buy Upgrade — Tap upgrade button
  Prestige — Tap prestige button (with confirmation)
  Navigate — Swipe between tabs / tap tab buttons
```

## MCP Integration
Unity MCP at `http://localhost:8080/mcp`. Use for UI screen building and build configuration.
